### Block dynamic hosts
/([0-9]{7,}|[0-9\.-_]{1,}range[0-9\.-_]{1,}|[0-9\.-_]{1,}ip[0-9\.-_]{1,}|rev|isdn|sta|dyn|unassigned|dial|modem|wireless|wifi|gprs|cdma|multi|dedicated|client|colo|share|static|subnet|broadband|in-addr|dhcp|ppp|pool|cable|static|dsl|dynamic|[0-9]{1,3}[-\._]{1,}[a-z]{,2}[0-9]{1,3}[-\._]{1,}[a-z]{,2}[0-9]{1,3}.*[a-z]|[a-z].*[0-9]{1,3}[-\._]{1,}[a-z]{,2}[0-9]{1,3}[-\._]{1,}[a-z]{,2}[0-9]{1,3}).*\..*\..*/ xMESSAGEx
/\..*[0-9]{3,}.*\..*[0-9]{3,}.*\..*[a-z0-9]{4,}.*\.[a-z]{2,3}$/				xMESSAGEx
